<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='653' id='t-653'>Hi. So today, I'd like to share
some works in progress.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='3953' id='t-3953'>Since we are still realizing these works,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='6170' id='t-6170'>we are largely working within the realm</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='7921' id='t-7921'>of intuition and mystery, still.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='10026' id='t-10026'>So I'm going to try and describe</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='11789' id='t-11789'>some of the experiences that we're looking for</span>
