</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 1:58
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='107541' id='t-107541'>So this brings me to a quieter, small work</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='110039' id='t-110039'>called Handheld.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='111608' id='t-111608'>The viewer sees a piece of paper</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='113342' id='t-113342'>that's mounted on the far end of the wall,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='115812' id='t-115812'>but when you go closer, you see that it's a blank</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='118440' id='t-118440'>A4, or a letter-sized piece of paper,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='120712' id='t-120712'>that's held on either side</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='122029' id='t-122029'>by two small hands</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='123970' id='t-123970'>that appear to be carved with a great deal</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='126237' id='t-126237'>of attention and care from a small block of wood.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='129710' id='t-129710'>The viewer also sees that this entire sculpture</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='132706' id='t-132706'>is sort of moving very slightly,</span>
