<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='163544' id='t-163544'>of an observer and a subjective point of view.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='166031' id='t-166031'>So we've just removed the camera</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='167860' id='t-167860'>and transferred that movement onto the panel.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='170141' id='t-170141'>So here's a video.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='171674' id='t-171674'>You have to imagine the other hand.
It's not there yet.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='174113' id='t-174113'>But to us, we're sort of trying to evoke</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='176860' id='t-176860'>a self-effacing gesture, as if there's a little person</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='180399' id='t-180399'>with outstretched arms</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='181990' id='t-181990'>behind this enormous piece of paper.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='184492' id='t-184492'>That sort of likens it to the amount of strain</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='187077' id='t-187077'>to be at the service of the observer and present</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='189381' id='t-189381'>this piece of paper very delicately to the viewer</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='192631' id='t-192631'>in front of them.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 3:26
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='195394' id='t-195394'>The next work is Decoy.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='197554' id='t-197554'>This is a cardboard model, so the object</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='199342' id='t-199342'>is about as tall as I am.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='201246' id='t-201246'>It has a rounded body, two arms,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='203135' id='t-203135'>and a very tall, head-like antenna,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='205346' id='t-205346'>and its sole purpose is to
